            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Fixed
- Bug fixes and improvements: when an agent asks you a question, the
  notification now shows the question instead of Allow/Deny buttons that
  couldn't answer it; session state tracking is more reliable when several
  agents report at once; and a brief push-service hiccup no longer drops a
  "needs you" alert.
]]></description>
